sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>6379/TCP GCS<br/>8265/TCP Dashboard
    participant WorkerPod as Ray Worker Pods

    Note over User,WorkerPod: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: kubeconfig
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event (RayCluster created)<br/>Service Account Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Service Account Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Service Account Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Services<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Service Account Token
    K8sAPI->>Registry: Pull Ray Image<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Pull Secret
    Registry-->>K8sAPI: Ray Container Image
    K8sAPI-->>HeadPod: Start Head Pod (ray start --head)
    K8sAPI-->>WorkerPod: Start Worker Pods (ray start)
    WorkerPod->>HeadPod: Register with GCS<br/>TCP/6379 (plaintext)
    HeadPod-->>WorkerPod: Worker Registered

    Note over User,WorkerPod: Flow 2: RayJob Submission

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply RayJob CR<br/>Auth: kubeconfig
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event (RayJob created)<br/>Service Account Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster (if needed)<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    Operator->>HeadPod: Submit Job via Dashboard API<br/>HTTP/8265 (plaintext)
    HeadPod->>WorkerPod: Distribute Tasks<br/>TCP/6379 GCS
    WorkerPod-->>HeadPod: Task Results
    HeadPod-->>Operator: Job Status
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update RayJob Status<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+

    Note over User,WorkerPod: Flow 3: Ray Serve Request

    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Ingress/Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant ServeSvc as Ray Serve Service<br/>8000/TCP HTTP

    Client->>Ingress: POST /predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: Application-defined
    Ingress->>ServeSvc: Forward Request<br/>HTTP/8000 (plaintext)
    ServeSvc->>HeadPod: GCS Lookup<br/>TCP/6379
    HeadPod-->>ServeSvc: Route to Serve Replica
    ServeSvc-->>Ingress: Prediction Response
    Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response
